Cozy with Creative Menu Perfect lunch stop on a road trip.  Small, friendly, casual, creative in decor and menu.  Opened by Carmella 8 years ago, her love of cooking is apparent in the fresh salads, dressings, soups and creative sandwiches and panninis.  Close to I-40, don't hesitate to stop.

Be sure not to miss gyro night on Wednesday and pizza night on Thursday with delivery to the brewery next door and wine bar across the street it's a no brainer.
